Stable Diffusion only supports resolutions that are multiples of 64. Keep that in mind when setting {Upscale Multiplier} for Upscaling in [Second Pass] to non-integer values, especially when working with multiple subjects.
{Upscale Multiplier} in the [Upscale Result] can be set to anything as there are no additional operations in latent space afterwards

{Choose Preset} in [Quality Prompt] is floored, so 1.5 counts as 1 and so on



The grid size for this workflow is 25
